Re EnronOnline due diligence Cc attached presentations as requested Regards Justin Mark Schroeder To Justin CT Amita CT cc Steven J ES Joe NRON Chris NRON Richard ES Subject EnronOnline due diligence JustinAmita I just got off a conference call with some of my colleagues in the States who deal with public policy issues for Enron in the US and abroad We talked about some emerging issues in ecommerce I told them about your excellent presentation on Monday on some of the issues that arise in due diligence for new EnronOnline products and even though it is not directly on point with some of their issues I think they all felt it would be enlightening to at least have the benefit of a copy of your presentation May I ask one of you to send a copy by email of your presentation materials to the other addressees on this email thanks mcs
